Class Tuple

  • java.lang.Object
    • Tuple

  • public class Tuple
extends java.lang.Object
    This class creates an ordered array of int elements which can be updated, added together, and described in multiple ways.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      Tuple(int numberOfDenominations)
      A constructor which takes in an int and creates a zeroed out Tuple with the length specified.

      A constructor which takes in an array of values and builds a new Tuple from this array.
